{"article_id":"L19GVXjUH5pDXKiB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Fighting to salvage his U.S. Supreme Court nomination ,","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh angrily denied on Thursday a university professor ' s accusation","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"that he sexually assaulted her 36 years ago","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"in a day of dramatic testimony","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"that gripped the country .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"her voice","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"sometimes cracking with emotion ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"appeared in public for the first time","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"to detail her allegation against Kavanaugh , a conservative federal appeals court judge","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"chosen by President Donald Trump for a lifetime job on the top U.S. court .","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"Ford told the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"she feared","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Kavanaugh would rape and accidentally kill her during the alleged assault in 1982 ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"when both were high school students in Maryland .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"She said","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"she was \" 100 percent certain \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"it was Kavanaugh who assaulted her .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Kavanaugh testified","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"after Ford finished her appearance ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"claiming","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"he was the victim of \" grotesque and obvious character assassination \"","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"orchestrated by Senate Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"he \" unequivocally and categorically \" denied Ford ' s allegation","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and vowed","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"he would not back down .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"\" I will not be intimidated into withdrawing from this process , \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Kavanaugh added .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Although they were at no point in the hearing room together ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"the clash pitted his word against hers .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"The almost nine hours of intensely emotional testimony came against the backdrop of the # MeToo movement against sexual harassment and assault","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and had millions of Americans riveted to their TV screens and smart phones .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Ford has emerged in the eyes of many American women as a compelling figure in the # MeToo movement","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that is usually associated less with the names of victims and more with a list of high-profile men","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"accused of misconduct .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"It was not clear , however , if the drama changed the views of any senators .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"The Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"controlled 51-49 by Trump ' s fellow Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"must now decide whether to vote to confirm Kavanaugh after the extraordinary nearly nine-hour hearing .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"Four senators","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"- Republicans Susan Collins , Lisa Murkowski and Jeff Flake along with Democrat Joe Manchin -","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"are seen as possible swing voters","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"whose decisions will determine","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"whether Kavanaugh is approved or rejected .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Kavanaugh was nominated by President Donald Trump","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"and his confirmation would cement conservative control of the Supreme Court with disputes over abortion rights , immigration , gay rights , voting rights and transgender troops","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"possibly heading toward the justices soon .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"The Judiciary Committee ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"on which Republicans hold an 11-10 majority ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"was to meet on Friday morning","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"and several senators said","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"they expected it to vote then .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"The full Senate could vote within days .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Writing on Twitter after the hearing ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Trump said of Kavanaugh :","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"\" His testimony was powerful , honest , and riveting .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Democrats ' search and destroy strategy is disgraceful","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"and this process has been a total sham and effort","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"to delay , obstruct , and resist .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"The Senate must vote ! \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Kavanaugh at times choked back tears ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"especially when he mentioned","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that his daughter suggested","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"they pray for Ford ,","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"when he spoke of his father","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"and when he mentioned women friends","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"who had rallied to support him .","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"Kavanaugh sharply attacked Democratic senators ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"calling himself the victim of \" a calculated and orchestrated political hit \"","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"fueled by anger on the left at Trump ' s 2016 election win over Democrat Hillary Clinton , his conservative judicial record , and revenge on behalf of Clinton and her husband , former President Bill Clinton .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"\" I swear today , under oath , before the Senate and the nation , before my family and God ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"I am innocent of this charge , \"","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"Kavanaugh told the Judiciary Committee .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Ford , a psychology professor at Palo Alto University in California , said","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"over four hours of testimony","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that a drunken Kavanaugh attacked her","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"and tried to remove her clothing at a gathering of teenagers","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"when he was 17 years old","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"and she was 15 .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"\" With what degree of certainty do you believe","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh assaulted you ? \"","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"Democratic Senator Dick Durbin asked Ford .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"\" One hundred percent , \"","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"she replied ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"remaining firm and unruffled even under questioning by a sex crimes prosecutor","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"hired by the committee ' s Republicans .","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"When Democratic Senator Dianne Feinstein asked her","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"if it could be a case of mistaken identity ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"as Kavanaugh and some Republican senators have suggested ,","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"Ford replied :","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"\" Absolutely not \" .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"U.S. Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh testifies before a Senate Judiciary Committee confirmation hearing for Kavanaugh on Capitol Hill in Washington , U.S. , September 27 , 2018 .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"/","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"Jim Bourg Murkowski , one of the three moderate Republican senators","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"who have not announced","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"whether or not they will support Kavanaugh ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"told :","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"\" I find Dr. Ford ' s testimony to be credible . \"","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"For his part , Kavanaugh testified","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"he was \" 100 percent certain \"","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"none of the alleged incidents of sexual misconduct occurred .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Democrats lauded Ford ' s testimony as credible , brave and , in the words of Senator Cory Booker , \" nothing short of heroic . \"","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"\" I want to thank you for your courage .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"And I want to tell you","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"I believe you . ...","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"And I believe","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"many Americans across the country believe you , \"","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"Democratic Senator Kamala Harris said .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"While some Republicans and Trump have called the allegations by Ford and the two other women part of a smear campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Ford told the committee","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"she had no political motivation ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"adding :","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"\" I am an independent person","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"and I am no one ' s pawn . \"","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Ford was seated at a table in the packed hearing room","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"flanked by her lawyers ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"facing a bank of senators .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"She told the senators","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"she was \" terrified \" to testify","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"but felt","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"it was her civic duty to come forward .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"\" Brett groped me","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"and tried to take off my clothes .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"He had a hard time","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"because he was very inebriated","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"and because I was wearing a one-piece bathing suit under my clothing .","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"I believed","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"he was going to rape me .","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"I tried to yell for help , \"","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"Ford said ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"that Kavanaugh and a friend of his , Mark Judge , were \" drunkenly laughing during the attack . \"","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Democratic senators sought to score political points during their five minutes apiece","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"of questioning Ford .","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"The panel ' s Republican senators , all men , did not question her ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"assigning that task to Rachel Mitchell , a sex crimes prosecutor .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"While Mitchell probed Ford ' s account","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"looking for gaps ,","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"her questioning seemed disjointed .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"She took turns with the Democratic senators","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"to ask questions in five-minute segments ,","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"disrupting her flow .","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"During Kavanaugh ' s testimony , Republican senators sidelined Mitchell","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"and asked their own questions .","depth":7},{"id":146,"text":"The bitter fight over Kavanaugh ' s nomination is unfolding just weeks before the Nov. 6 congressional elections","depth":5},{"id":147,"text":"in which Democrats are trying to seize majority control of Congress from the Republicans .","depth":5},{"id":148,"text":"It has also deepened the country ' s political polarization .","depth":4},{"id":149,"text":"Kavanaugh ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"sitting alone at the witness table ,","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"he wanted to testify","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"as soon as Ford ' s allegation emerged last week","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"and was not surprised","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"other allegations followed .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"\" In those 10 long days ,","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"as was predictable","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"and as I predicted ,","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"my family and my name have been totally and permanently destroyed by vicious and false additional accusations , \"","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"as his wife sat behind him .","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"Kavanaugh repeatedly tangled with Democratic senators ,","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"interrupting several of them ,","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"including Feinstein and Amy Klobuchar ,","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"during testy exchanges .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"When Klobuchar asked him about his teenage drinking ,","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"he threw the question back at her ,","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"asking her","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"whether she had ever been blackout drunk .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"He later apologized for the question .","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"Kavanaugh was careful not to denounce Ford ,","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"he wished her \" no ill will. \"","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"he was not questioning","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"that Ford may have been sexually assaulted by someone in some place at some time ,","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"but that he had never assaulted her or anyone else .","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"Some Democrats have called on Kavanaugh to withdraw in light of the allegations .","depth":6},{"id":179,"text":"At the hearing , Republican Senator Lindsey Graham castigated Democratic senators ,","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"seeking to rally Republicans not to abandon the nominee .","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"\" This is the most unethical sham","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"since I ' ve been in politics , \"","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"Graham said .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"Ford said","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"Kavanaugh put his hand over her mouth","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"to stop her from screaming during the assault .","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"She added :","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"\" This was what terrified me the most ,","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"and has had the most lasting impact on my life .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"It was hard for me to breathe ,","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"and I thought","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"that Brett was accidentally going to kill me . \"","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"Her strongest memory of the incident ,","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"Ford said ,","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"was the \" uproarious laughter between the two","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"( Kavanaugh and Judge )","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"and their having fun at my expense. \"","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"She said","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"the laughter had haunted her ever since .","depth":10},{"id":200,"text":"Two other women , Deborah Ramirez and Julie Swetnick , have accused Kavanaugh of sexual misconduct in the 1980s .","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"Ramirez accused Kavanaugh of exposing himself during a drunken dormitory party during the 1983-84 academic year","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"when both attended Yale University .","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"Swetnick said","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"she witnessed efforts by Kavanaugh and others","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"to get girls drunk at parties","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"so they could be raped .","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"She said","depth":9},{"id":208,"text":"Kavanaugh was present at a 1982 party","depth":10},{"id":209,"text":"where she was raped .","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"who has himself faced accusations of sexual misconduct ,","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"chose Kavanaugh","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"to succeed Justice Anthony Kennedy ,","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"who retired effective in July .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":429,"left":0,"right":428,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":428,"left":359,"right":427,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":359,"left":306,"right":358,"relation":"elaboration